UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I thank you, $N.  You\'ve shown a great deal of goodwill towards my clan.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12471; -- Cruelty of the Kvaldir
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='The dead are honored by your actions, $N.$B$B<The wounded orc nods and exhales slowly.>$B$BPerhaps now I can find my way back to being the warrior I once was.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11639; -- Revenge Upon Magmoth
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I am freed. Thank you, $N.$B$BAnd now, I have one final request of you.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11637; -- Kaganishu
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='They\'ve shackled his spirit. $N, we have to put an end to his torture!$B$BYou must descend into the bowels of Magmoth and find a way to free him!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11631; -- Vision of Air
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Regrettable, but necessary. I\'ll take the claw, $N.$B$BThank you for all of the help you\'ve given us. With Claximus defeated, maybe we\'ll be able to reunite the remaining murlocs and seal off those caverns.$B$BPlease, my friend, take this... it\'s the least I can do for all of the help you have rendered us!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11566; -- Surrender... Not!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Now no matter what happens, the Winterfin murlocs have a secure future.$B$BYou are to be commended, and rewarded, for your selflessness, $N!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11560; -- Oh Noes, the Tadpoles!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11702; -- King Mrgl-Mrgl
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='The ancestors have found their statues, and they have you to thank, $N. The craftsmen of Kaskala will return to the quarry and ensure that the line of ancestors continues unbroken. For our part, the ancestors will continue to observe you with interest, as it seems your path is just beginning.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11610; -- Leading the Ancestors Home
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='The curator and his men must\'ve thought the quarry an easy target for their looting, but you\'ve shown them otherwise, $N. I am deeply grateful for your help and I\'m certain the ancestors will continue to watch over you.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11623; -- A Visit to the Curator
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I can sense the upheaval in the spirit world beginning to calm. You have done well, $N. The spirits of the ancestors are fortunate to have your help in this time of need.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11607; -- The Lost Spirits
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Now that these strange mages know that the people of Kaskala and their allies will not give up the quarry so easily, we must maintain our efforts and defeat them completely.$B$BMy brothers in Kaskala have also come under attack and will not be able to support us, but with your help, $N, we can overcome these pillagers.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11612; -- Reclaiming the Quarry
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Elder Atkanok\'s voice greets you as you approach his statue.>$B$BWell done, $N. With the names of the wandering elders, we can continue the ceremonies disrupted during the attack. However, before the elders\' spirits can be led to their stones, we must calm the spirits of the murdered craftsmen and shaman. Otherwise, the ancestor spirits may never hear the ceremony\'s call.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11605; -- The Honored Ancestors
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Excellent work, $N. We are closing in on Nesingwary!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11872; -- The Nefarious Clam Master...
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='A job well done, $N. Now we strike at the pirate leader!\n', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11871; -- Not On Our Watch
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<You hear a voice in your head. It is Khu\'nok.>$B$BYour name has been heard in the whistling winds, $N. You have done a great thing for my kin. For this we will consider you an ally. Alas, our torment cannot end without bloodshed and violence.$B$BThe price of peace for the mammoths will be the death of Kaw...\n', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11878; -- Khu'nok Will Know
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You do the Earth Mother\'s work, $N, but do not revel in this victory for too long. We have discovered the hiding place of the trapper leader.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11865; -- Unfit for Death
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I thank you, $N.  These supplies will feed our cousins and children.  Even if Kaskala falls, our tribes must carry on.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11945; -- Preparing for the Worst
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='I feared they might\'ve captured Grumm, but I never thought they\'d do such horrific things to him. I\'ve never seen a warrior survive a losing battle with the Scourge.$B$BThank you for bringing word of his fate, $N. He was a mighty warrior and we will remember him as such.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11659; -- Shatter the Orbs!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='<The taunka snow tracker appears weak and barely responds to you.>$B$BI haven\'t... long. Maybe... maybe you can stop them... before...', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11654; -- The Spire of Blood
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='What word do you bring from Highmesa?$B$B<You explain what you know and give the greatmother the bad news concerning Longrunner Bristlehorn.>$B$BMy... my grandson!$B$B<The greatmother fights to keep control of her emotions.>$B$BHe died an honorable death like a true taunka!$B$BYou were the last to be with him, $N, so he shall always be a part of you. I give you my thanks for completing his last wishes.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11689; -- Return with the Bad News
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thank you, $N.$B$BThe Lich King and his Scourge are a blight upon Northrend. We must not stop until they are all truly dead, and his existence is put to an end!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11683; -- Fallen Necropolis
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thank you, $N.$B$BWith these odd creatures destroyed, dealing with the rest of the pools should now be a simple matter.$B$BWe owe you a debt of gratitude.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11907; -- The Sub-Chieftains
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<The greatmother breathes a heavy sigh of relief.>$B$BIt is done then... you have saved us! If you hadn\'t stopped him here, then who knows how far this mistake of the gnomes would have spread?$B$BWith the threats from the blue dragons and the Nexus War, not to mention the Lich King, the last thing we need is a mad creation of the Titans running loose!$B$BThank you, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11909; -- Defeat the Gearmaster
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Barah accepts the pieces of the horn from you and begins trying to fit them together.>$B$BStormhoof would be proud of you, $N. Perhaps when we\'ve dealt with the Scourge, I will take the horn with me on a pilgrimage to Stormhoof\'s tomb.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11695; -- The Horn of Elemental Fury
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I feel the power of the storm coursing through you!$B$BYou are ready, $N. Let us begin.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11895; -- Master the Storm
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Hellscream picks up the head of Gammothra with one arm and spits in its face.>$B$BThey will learn, $N... They will all learn. The Horde is not to be trifled with...', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11722; -- Trophies of Gammoth
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=274, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11724; -- Massive Moth Omelet?
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='A job well done, $N! Would you honor Laurith and I by taking the head of the beast and presenting it to Hellscream? He will be extremely pleased.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11721; -- Gammothra the Tormentor
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='A job well done, $N! Thank you!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11714; -- Vermin Extermination
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Good job, $N. That\'s one less filthy, useless, Alliance scum-bag that we\'ll have to provide for...$B$BIf you\'re lookin\' for more work, the tauren and blood elf nearby need some help.$B$B\'Course we\'ve got our own set of problems to deal with out here as well...\n', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11711; -- Coward Delivery... Under 30 Minutes or it's Free
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=25, `Emote4`=273, `EmoteDelay1`=1000, `EmoteDelay2`=1000, `EmoteDelay3`=1000, `EmoteDelay4`=1000, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11632; -- What the Cold Wind Brings...
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='At least for now the rhinos will know peace. Thank you, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11884; -- Nedar, Lord of Rhinos...
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Blood and thunder! You\'ve salvaged our newborn relations with the taunka.$B$BThank you for putting the situation to rights. Aka\'Magosh, $N!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11592; -- We Strike!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Oh my goodness, you made it! I was uncertain.$B$BYou flickered in and out of the time stream there for a moment during the fight! I thought for sure that we\'d lost you!$B$BBut here you are safe and sound, with your past self rescued, on the other side of the time loop you were in.$B$BYou\'re quite the temporal $g hero : heroine;, $N!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=13343; -- Mystery of the Infinite, Redux
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Excellent. Just as I suspected all along. I shall have to attempt to contact Ysera and see if she approves.$B$BIf she can be coaxed from her nightmare, of course.$B$BThank you, $N. You have been indispensable.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12459; -- That Which Creates Can Also Destroy
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Let\'s see them bring her back to life without her head!$B$B<The high executor\'s laugh draws a number of furtive glances.>$B$BI\'m a little concerned that you let this grand admiral get away, but you\'re still the $g hero : heroine; of the day, $N!$B$BTake your pick... you\'ve earned it!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12285; -- Do Unto Others
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='My father was right about you, $N. Everything that he said has come to pass - only one final duty remains unfulfilled. I will now lead the Kor\'kron to the front line. The time to end this war is at hand. The Lich King\'s tyranny ends today!$B$BTake my post now, $N, and stand guard over our forces.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12500; -- Return To Angrathar
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I knew that you would return, $N. You have served the Wyrmrest Accord and saved your people from certain death. Let it be known to all and let it be recorded for posterity!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12498; -- On Ruby Wings
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Back so soon, $N?$B$BVargastrasz sent word ahead of you. Thank you for what you did at the Ruby Dragonshrine.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12769; -- The Steward of Wyrmrest Temple
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You must be $N. I was told you\'d be coming.$B$B<The ambassador grunts.>$B$BI have something that I want you to take care of. If you do, you\'ll prove yourself to the dragons here.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12767; -- Speak with your Ambassador
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Lok\'tar ogar! I have heard much about you, $N. Your battle scars run deep - a testament to your dedication and power!$B$BWith the flanking attacks of the Lich King crushed in both the west and east, only the forces at the gate remain. We gain ground each day, soon to break through this wall and into Icecrown!$B$BOnce we stop the skeletal dragons, Highlord Fordragon and I will take the field.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12224; -- The Kor'kron Vanguard!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Gort takes the tome from you and begins reading.>$B$BWHAT! This can\'t be right. I\'ve known some of these orcs for years!$B$BLeave me, $N. I have much work to do and many traitors to execute.$B$BTake one of these items for your trouble. You\'ve done a great service for the Horde this day.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12136; -- The Translated Tome
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Doctor Malefious looks through the contents of the package.>$B$BGlorious! Exactly to specifications!$B$BHere is your payment, $N. Keep what you\'ve seen and done to yourself. This work is all classified - information is given out on a need to know basis.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12221; -- The Forsaken Blight
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='The power I hold comes at a great cost, $N. Many knights, light and dark alike, lost their lives in the final battle at Light\'s Hope. The prospect of the future looks grim, but at least now I know what I face. The Lich King will never release his grasp and for that alone he must die!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12132; -- The Power to Destroy
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I can already feel the cold coursing through me, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12127; -- In Service of Frost
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I knew my sister wouldn\'t let us down.$B$BWell done, $N. The Onslaught\'s lumbermill will be out of commission for a while, which means no new construction or ballistae.$B$BThanks for helping me to live up to the family name.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12240; -- A Means to an End
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<You think you see just the hint of a smile cross Wroth\'s face before quickly disappearing.>$B$BYou\'re now my favorite $c, $N. If you have a mind to, I\'d like you to think about joining up as an officer in the Hand of Vengeance.$B$BWe can start you out as a deathguard, and in a few decades I think you have what it takes to make junior executor!$B$BNo? Well don\'t be too hasty... take your time and mull it over.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12273; -- The Denouncement
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Alphonse had it you say? That makes sense.$B$BI recognize it from my youthful days as a torturer in the court of King Terenas of fallen Lordaeron. It\'s known as a rod of compulsion.$B$B<The high executor wrings his hands together in evil anticipation of what\'s to come.>$B$BI have an idea for how we can make good use of it!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12271; -- The Rod of Compulsion
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='What? You were expecting us to have you rescue them?$B$BNow why would we do that when they have a proven track record of getting themselves captured in the first place?$B$BNorthrend is a cold place, young $N. I suggest that you adjust to it.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12245; -- No Mercy for the Captured
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You spoke with Oacha\'noa?!$B$BIf it is her will that we stand with your people then so be it. Elder Ko\'nani will accept this as our destiny, for weal or woe.$B$BMy people believe that all souls are one with the magic of the world. We must oppose the blue dragon attempts to control the magic or we are all doomed!$B$BI never thought that a $r would be the champion of the Kalu\'ak, but you have proven me wrong. On behalf of my people, I give you thanks, $N.$B$BMay the gods smile upon you and keep you safe.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12032; -- Conversing With the Depths
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You have done an honorable thing, $N. Please, choose a reward.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12111; -- Where the Wild Things Roam
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='How very odd that it imprinted this information upon you magically.$B$BSo, not only do we know that they\'ve redirected the flow of the power coming out of the Moonrest Gardens, but we now know that the power is being purposefully changed in some way. Just what are they up to with all of that magic?$B$BI don\'t like where this is leading, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12066; -- The Focus on the Beach
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You are a brave $c, $N. You\'ve done the Horde a great service by rescuing the High Chief.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12069; -- Return of the High Chief
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='These are in excellent condition, $N. I\'ll get to work right away. If anything comes of this, you will be the first to know!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12048; -- Scourge Armaments
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='It\'s so light... As if it weighs nothing at all! I\'ll need time to analyze the metal and see if I can do anything with it! Tests! I need to run tests!$B$BI\'ll keep in contact, $N. If anything comes of this, you\'ll be the first to know.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12039; -- Black Blood of Yogg-Saron
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Overlord Agmar looks over the document.>$B$BIs this what I think it is? With the information contained within these pages we will CRUSH the Anub\'ar assault!$B$BYou have done well to bring this document to me, $N. Perhaps you will be allowed to watch or even participate in the final battle at Angrathar! LOK\'TAR!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12041; -- The Lost Empire
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='$N, if I\'m not mistaken, you\'ve uncovered the key to allow us to discern exactly what the mage hunter forces are up to!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12059; -- A Strange Device
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thank you for doing this, Commander $N. They had nothing left. You have given them purpose and with purpose comes hope... Hope for a new tomorrow... for a new life.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11983; -- Blood Oath of the Horde
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='This is exactly what we need, $N! Brandishing Horde arms will lift their spirits and give them the protection they need against the Scourge.$B$BAre you prepared for the ceremony of initiation?$B$B<Brighthoof nods.>$B$BYou will be the one to admit our new allies into the Horde.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11978; -- Into the Fold
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Roh\'kill salutes you.>$B$BYou have preserved our honor, $N. Tor\'zin and I both thank you for this selfless act!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11980; -- Pride of the Horde
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11979; -- The Taunka and the Tauren
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=6, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11996; -- Your Presence is Required at Agmar's Hammer
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='This will do nicely, $N. Did those pathetic whelps put up a fight or did they just shower you with ghostly tears of sorrow?$B$BAh, they get so emotional...', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12188; -- The Forsaken Blight and You: How Not to Die
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Can\'t you just see it now, $c? It\'ll be the vacation spot of Northrend!$B$BWhat do you think of the name, \"Hansen\'s Cove\", or maybe \"$N Bay\"? Kind of catchy, don\'t you think?', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12304; -- Beachfront Property
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12182; -- To Venomspite!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12181; -- Give it a Name
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Fifteen down, eh? Good to hear it, $c.$b$bIf nothing else you\'ve bought us a bit of time - at least a day by my figuring.$b$bHere\'s your pay.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12284; -- Keep 'Em on Their Heels
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Oh, thank you, thank you.$b$bYou\'ve helped us to live another day. Perhaps there\'s hope yet.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12288; -- Overwhelmed!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=1, `RewardText`='Good work, soldier!$b$bNow take this key and get yourself down to Venture Bay. It\'ll let you use one of the refurbished shredders to unleash chaos on our enemies.$b$bOh yes, and talk to Darrok if you want to take the shortcut!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12270; -- Shred the Alliance
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thanks, $n. That should keep me going - at least until tomorrow....$b$bHere\'s the cash I promised.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12280; -- Making Repairs
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='What happened today... had to happen.  It doesn\'t mean I have to be happy about it.$B$BI\'ve freed my people from a tyrant, but I\'ve also lost a sister.  I thank you for your help, $N.  I wish to be alone now.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12431; -- The Conquest Pit: Final Showdown
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Not bad, $N.  You might be slightly more useful than I initially thought.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12413; -- Attack on Silverbrook
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Could it be?  The man who wrote this journal feared for his daughters\' lives so he sent them away from Silverbrook.$B$BWe just captured an outcast in the outskirts of town about the same age as the eldest daughter.$B$BListen, $N.  There\'s more happening here than meets the eye... we can\'t just burn this diary.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12424; -- Gorgonna
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Nice job, $N.  These will feed two or three grunts each.  Not bad.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12436; -- Supplemental Income
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12315; -- Crush Captain Brightwater!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well done, $N.  Our control over the logging camp might not be complete yet, but thanks to you we\'re one step closer to smashing these Alliance worms.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12170; -- Blackriver Brawl
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `Emote2`=1, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12317; -- Keep Them at Bay
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=113, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12324; -- Smoke 'Em Out
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=1, `RewardText`='Well done!$b$b<Mack laughs hysterically for a moment.>$b$bAww, come on now. That was funny...hic.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12038; -- Seared Scourge
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thank you, $N.  I\'ll take those from you.$B$BThe corruptive power of these seeds is dangerous.  I must destroy them right away.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12242; -- Vordrassil's Seeds
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I can\'t make any promises, $N.  But I will try my best to purify these.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12241; -- Destroy the Sapling
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `Emote2`=1, `Emote3`=1, `Emote4`=273, `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12763; -- Shifting Priorities
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='We got him good, $N.  But not good enough.$B$BOne thing\'s for sure... we won\'t be seeing him around these parts any longer.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12164; -- Hour of the Worg
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='So it\'s an uncertain thing? I wish it was not a matter of chance, but at least we\'re on the right path. Without your help, this wouldn\'t have ever been possible. Should you learn any more about the machinations of the iron dwarves and their plans toward the children of stone, seek us out and we will hear you, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12099; -- Free at Last
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='<Soulok nods in approval.>$B$BWell done, $N. We must not let the Alliance gain any kind of advantage.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12415; -- The Horse Hollerer
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='This blood carries the same taint as the slime you obtained earlier... this does not bode well, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12229; -- A Possible Link
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well done, $N. The loss of the iron dwarf commander should be enough to break the remaining defenders. The Earthen should be able to deal with the survivors.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=11985; -- Into the Breach
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Well done, $N. I\'ll prepare the incense and then we\'ll see what exactly this royal dwarf was doing so far from home.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12054; -- Deciphering the Journal
