UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='That\'s it! That\'s the first half of Norgannon\'s keystone. Well done, $N. I\'ve had Archaeologist Andorin on the lookout for clues to the shell\'s whereabouts for a long time. He\'s never going to believe me when I tell him it was an intrepid $r who found it instead.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12928; -- Norgannon's Shell
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='We\'re here, $N.  My brother\'s forces will learn the meaning of defeat today.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=13057; -- The Terrace of the Makers
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Yes... these will do.  Let us hope my plan works, $N.$B$BVeranus is a great drake.  I\'d hate to have to settle for a lesser one.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=13050; -- Veranus
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You continue to prove yourself worthy.  We are honored by your presence.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=13423; -- Defending Your Title
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `Emote1`=5, `RewardText`='I like you. In fact, you rock!$B$BYay for you!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12833; -- Overstock
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thanks, $N!  We\'ll see what we can do to salvage these parts!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12844; -- Equipment Recovery
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Unbelievable! This will be a story for the ages, $N! One $g man:woman; rode upon the head of the king of storm giants and decimated an entire Scourge army!$B$BAnd I was there to see it all happen...', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12919; -- The Storm King's Vengeance
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='So, now ya be seein\' what we be up against, mon.$b$bI want ya ta go down, learn da land, mingle with yer bretheren. Prepare yourself...$b$bSoon, dere be much for ya to do. Don\'t ya be disappointin\' me!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12664; -- Dark Horizon
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You did it, $N! That was the most exciting fight yet! What are you going to do with your winnings? Me? I\'m going to Dalaran and blowing it all in the Underbelly. Lot of hot action going on down there!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12948; -- The Champion of Anguish
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Damn, I remember Korrak from way back in my younger days when I used to work for the Frostwolf Clan. He would never shut up! I think you just did the world a great service, $N.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12936; -- The Amphitheater of Anguish: Korrak the Bloodrager!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='I was worried for a while there, $N. When he busted out the seals and penguins... Well, I didn\'t know what to think to be honest. It looked pretty damn ridiculous.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12935; -- The Amphitheater of Anguish: Tuskarrmageddon!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Yay! You\'re the best, $N!$B$BI wasn\'t looking forward to being sprayed with Scourge stuff, that\'s for sure! I guess it\'s going to be hard for those stupid nerubians to spread their evil now!$B$BHow about I give you a little something for saving my skin?', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12555; -- A Tangled Skein
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You\'re the $g hero : heroine; of the hour, $N.$B$B<Moonshard kicks the head away from him.>$B$BYou deserve our deepest respect, and something more I think.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12554; -- Malas the Corrupter
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Aw, me thinkin\' that too funny.$B$B$N is my kind of $r!$B$BYou still got my knife?', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12659; -- Scalps!
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You did it!$B$B<Dagoda gives you a big kiss on the cheek.>$B$BYou have no idea how much of a relief that is to me! Defending against trolls on all sides is really putting a strain on us. Not to mention his incessant yelling.$B$BPlease, $N, take your pick of what we have to offer.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12662; -- Bringing Down Heb'Jin
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Very fine specimens indeed, $N! These are sure to provide many hours of curious speculation amongst my colleagues back home.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=13549; -- Tails Up
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You\'ve done what had to be done and honored me in the process.$B$BI give you my deepest thanks, $N. I only hope that you and Har\'koa will be able to help the others.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12647; -- An End to the Suffering
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Thank you, $N. I will never forget what you have done.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12632; -- But First My Offspring
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='You did it! $N, you are the champion of Zul\'Drak!$B$BWe will never be able to repay the debt that we owe to you, but the Zandalari have given into my trust a number of objects they believe you might have an interest in.$B$BPlease, I want you to have a token of our appreciation, but hurry. I sense another issue of urgency!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12730; -- Convocation at Zol'Heb
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Your bravery seems boundless, $N.$B$BPlease hand me the heart and the essence, and I will fashion them into that which will compel the prophet to appear before you.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12729; -- The Gods Have Spoken
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='No!$B$BAnother god destroyed, its power stolen. And now the prophet of Akali has threatened us directly.$B$BWhen he comes, he will come for Har\'koa. We cannot allow him to take her power too.$B$BWe must consult the gods once more, $N. They will tell us what must be done.', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12721; -- Rampage
UPDATE `quest_offer_reward` SET `RewardText`='Just look at all of that!$B$BSee here, $N. This piece you recovered vividly illustrates that the Drakkari became aware of the weakening of the land that the Scourge caused by their presence.$B$BThe warlord felt compelled to take the opportunity this presented. He pushed the prophets to kill their gods in an effort to control the power and fight back against the Lich King\'s forces.$B$BEither way they were doomed. They inadvertently chose to be the instrument of their own destruction!', `VerifiedBuild`=59185 WHERE `ID`=12709; -- Hexed Caches

